edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.filter

Interface SeededFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SeededWatershedFilter

    public interface SeededFilter
    Describes filters that operate using a seed Image.

    Conceptually this should be distinct from a reference image in that the seed Image should be a mask identifying regions using some other means that will guide the SeededFilter.

    Author:
    Colin J. Fuller
